public class DeliveryProcessDescriptionImpl
extends ProcessDescriptionImpl
implements DeliveryProcessDescription
An implementation of the model object 'Delivery Process Description'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Scale
  • Project Characteristics
  • Risk Level
  • Estimating Technique
  • Project Member Expertise
  • Type Of Contract
